title: 2015 BKYSC Holiday Fundraiser
desc: Please Join Us... BKYSC is excited to invite you to attend the 2015 Annual Holiday Fundraiser, benefitting the after-school and summer programs at the Brooklyn Youth Sports Club. ?This year's event will be held on Friday, December 4th at Cipriani's Wall Street location.? A special thanks to the BKYSC Board of Directors as well as the many Event Chairs who make this event a great success every year. ?As always, thank you so much for your support and we look forward to seeing you on December 4th.
